{"article_id":"wxWFx14auXSYNcq2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A Black Hawk helicopter swoops in","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"to pick up Sgt . Bowe Bergdahl in a valley in Afghanistan ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"in a video of the handover of the American prisoner of war","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that was posted online early Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"The Pentagon says","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"it 's reviewing the video ;","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"a spokesman says","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"there 's no reason","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"to question its authenticity .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"The handover reportedly took place in eastern Afghanistan 's Khost province , near Pakistan .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"The video shows Bergdahl sitting in the back of a pickup truck ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"wearing white clothing .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"It also shows more than a dozen fighters","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"positioned around the valley .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"In the video , the Black Hawk helicopter lands","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"with its side facing the area","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"where Bergdahl and the Taliban fighters wait .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"As several people come out of the helicopter ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"the American is led toward them under a white flag .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Sky News has posted a raw version of the video","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that includes the original audio track , with few words in English","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"( updated at 12:20 p.m . ET :","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"the AP initially posted the video ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"but the agency has since withdrawn it ) .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"The exchange is over in seconds ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"as the participants hold up their hands to one another .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"The men","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"- three from the helicopter , and two from the Taliban force -","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"engage in quick handshakes ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"then they wave their farewells .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"All the while , the scene was being filmed ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"with the photographer featuring the figure of Bergdahl and the helicopter .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"`` We have no reason","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"to doubt the video 's authenticity ,","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"but we are reviewing it , ''","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Pentagon Press Secretary John Kirby says .","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"`` Regardless , we know","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"the transfer was peaceful and successful ,","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"and our focus remains on getting Sgt . Bergdahl the care","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"he needs . ''","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"The exchange of Bergdahl for five Taliban prisoners","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"held in Guantanamo Bay , Cuba ,","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"has sparked a series of questions","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"that range from the circumstances of the soldier 's capture in Afghanistan to the legality of the prisoner exchange -","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"members of Congress say","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"they were n't given advance notice of the deal .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"President Obama says","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"the White House had spoken `` for some time '' about a possible prisoner swap for Bergdahl ;","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"his administration says","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"it had to act quickly","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"to free him .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"A congressional hearing on the matter is slated for next week ,","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"NPR 's David Welna reports on today 's Morning Edition ;","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"more are expected to follow .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Yesterday , Secretary of the Army John McHugh said","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"the service is happy to have Bergdahl back .","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"He added","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"that the Army will conduct `` a comprehensive , coordinated effort","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"that will include speaking with Sgt . Bergdahl","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"to better learn from him the circumstances of his disappearance and captivity . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":119,"left":99,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":91,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":78,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":69,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":63,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":61,"right":62,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":61,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":64,"right":66,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":66,"left":6,"right":65,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":72,"right":76,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":70,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":74,"right":75,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":14,"right":73,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":90,"left":82,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nucleari